- `noosphere/noosphere/articles/transcript_enrichment.py`
- transcript/source-structure code in `theseus-codex/src/app/(authed)/transcripts/[uploadId]/`
- existing tests for ingestion, relevant text, transcript enrichment, and conclusions.

