1. Add an empirical case-study extraction contract:
   - concrete case id;
   - source span/chunk references;
   - actors;
   - institutions;
   - time period;
   - domain;
   - observed mechanism;
   - outcome;
   - stated causal claim;
   - uncertainty/evidence quality;
   - linked abstract principles.
2. Implement a typed model and extraction path for empirical cases.
   Prefer a package boundary such as:
   - `noosphere/noosphere/cases/`
   - or an existing ingestion/conclusions package if that is the codebase pattern.
